<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="illness-n">illness <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'ɪlnəs/    美 /'ɪlnəs/  </p>
<p>[C] &amp; [U]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-sickness">1.★ <strong>疾病 (sickness)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>suffer from a serious illness</strong>
患重病</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>recover from a</strong> severe <strong>illness</strong>
从大病中恢复过来</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>treat / prevent an illness
治疗/预防疾病</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>develop a rare illness
得一种罕见的病</p></div></div>